@startuml
title Alerts GET (Cursor Pagination)

actor Client
participant "API Gateway" as API
participant "Alerts Service" as Service
participant "Cache" as Cache
participant "Database" as DB

Client -> API : GET /v1/alerts?limit=25&cursor=abc
API -> Cache : Check cursor "abc"
Cache --> API : Cached data? Yes -> return subset
Cache --> API : No -> forward request
API -> Service : Fetch alerts from DB
Service -> DB : Query alerts after cursor "abc"
DB --> Service : Result set
Service --> Cache : Store result with cursor key
Service --> API : Return data + nextCursor
API --> Client : 200 OK (alerts list + nextCursor)
@enduml
